Dialogue: 5,0:00:01.81,0:00:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I suddenly saw my past self.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:05.90,0:00:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to save him, but he made himself fall.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.36,0:00:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anything like that happened since?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:12.36,0:00:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was just that one time.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:15.03,0:00:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.83,0:00:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, what's going to happen to me?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.58,0:00:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be sure right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.67,0:00:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prescribe a sedative for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:26.88,0:00:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it if you feel unstable again.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.97,0:00:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My past self returned once before.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.01,0:00:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While he was here, I was unconscious.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:44.48,0:00:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And while I'm conscious, he's not here.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:49.44,0:00:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's as if I'm fighting with my past self over the person called Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:57.16,0:01:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he chose to disappear into the darkness.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:02.75,0:01:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words, he won't try to take over my body again.
