Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.43,0:02:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the middle of September, I returned to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.64,0:02:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I brought with me a ring my mother gave me.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.56,0:02:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Banri!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wore this ring when I was younger.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.32,0:03:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have a girlfriend in Tokyo, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.74,0:03:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give it to her.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.12,0:03:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this looks pretty expensive.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.74,0:03:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:07.95,0:03:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure the ring will be happier if a young lady is wearing it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.55,0:03:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouko!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.56,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.64,0:03:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been such a long, long, super long time!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're looking well!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When we heard from you,\N we decided to come meet you!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.19,0:03:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been way too long.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Things just aren't right without you!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.66,0:03:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you people welcoming him home before me?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.75,0:03:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Know your place!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the moving reunion of two lovers!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.01,0:04:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That joke totally wasn't necessary!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home, Kouko.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.93,0:04:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, welcome, welcome home!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.81,0:04:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, a toast to Tada Banri-kun's return to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka-chan, you cut your hair.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.99,0:04:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. This is the first time you've seen it.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.83,0:04:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks great on you.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But wasn't it kind of a shame to cut it off?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.33,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... You agree with Yana and 2D-kun, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe cutting it {\i1}was{\i0} a mistake.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's a shame at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it looks great on you.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, shucks.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.01,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Banri and Kouko, I need a huge favor from you guys.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.44,0:04:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I could check out your club?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.23,0:05:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make a film about the Festival Club.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.57,0:05:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A film?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.45,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the school festival in November?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.53,0:05:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to produce something to show there.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.99,0:05:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of editing you guys dancing into a short film, like a music video.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka-chan, are you helping him?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.17,0:05:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've got other plans.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.67,0:05:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to ask the senior members about letting him film us.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:24.84,0:05:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the Festival Club, anyway?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.59,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to be honest, I'm interested in someone in the Festival Club.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to film...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.85,0:05:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I want to see Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.23,0:05:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping this would give me a chance to get closer to her.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.07,0:05:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We've actually gone out to eat together a few times,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's completely one-sided.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I panicked and did some weird things.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.95,0:05:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, I get it.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.17,0:06:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the reason, we'll talk to the senior members about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.71,0:06:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You just hang on to your one-sided crush and wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.59,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, guys.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.97,0:06:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.51,0:06:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So you knew?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.10,0:06:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We all saw you with Linda-senpai before.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.52,0:06:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.69,0:06:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't all making fun of my one-sided crush, were you?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.61,0:06:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought it'd be better if we didn't interfere.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was wrong of us, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.99,0:06:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.12,0:06:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell you guys about Linda-senpai
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.08,0:06:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,because there was something else on my mind that wasn't easy to explain.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.21,0:06:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually felt kind of jealous of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You were jealous of me?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.80,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, it looks like you and Linda-senpai aren't just in the same club.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like there's something else to your relationship.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.81,0:07:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When you were injured,\N Linda-senpai was really worried.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're both from Shizuoka, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.53,0:07:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I started thinking about it, everything started to bother me.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.91,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I even thought...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.70,0:07:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you might be hiding something important from me.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.83,0:07:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I started to suspect that you didn't really accept me.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:27.59,0:07:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be the only time I ask, so give me a straight answer.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:31.97,0:07:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri, is there something you're not telling me?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why don't I just tell him?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should be honest.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shouldn't hide anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.48,0:07:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Linda and I were classmates in high school, and I was in love with her.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.69,0:07:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I lost my memories and didn't recognize her when we met again.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.41,0:07:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've hurt Kouko before because I was confused about my feelings.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But now my mind is clear,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:03.42,0:08:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Linda and my family respect who I am now.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So everything is fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.76,0:08:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no problem.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, well...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There must really be something wrong with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:19.81,0:08:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for suspecting you of weird stuff like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.39,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you weren't...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I still want to be your friend.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.53,0:08:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.87,0:08:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad you didn't hurt yourself, Banri.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.04,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you something next time.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, right!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mom's ring!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that something I should give her so casually?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.88,0:08:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wouldn't giving her a ring mean... proposing?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.72,0:09:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If Kouko and I got married, I'd be ecstatic, of course!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if we did,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.68,0:09:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Kaga family fortune and her ramen-eating dad would come with it.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.94,0:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Plus, I wouldn't fit in as a member of the Kaga family. I just don't match.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:14.95,0:09:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe proposing to Kouko just because I love her is a bad idea.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.70,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Banri.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think this is?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... um...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my present to you.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.38,0:09:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you like it.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.13,0:09:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.01,0:09:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We were apart for a while, weren't we?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.10,0:09:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed you so much.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of you all the time,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but that made me love you even more.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.11,0:09:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd try to express my love artistically,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so I made this.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What do you think it is?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.49,0:10:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, a club?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not? Then, um...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Eiffel Tower.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.38,0:10:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.46,0:10:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What I'm saying is... you know!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.22,0:10:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided that when you came back,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.43,0:10:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd f-finally... make you let me become one with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.10,0:10:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.98,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, we'll finally climb the stu-ste-stairs to ada-ado-adulthood!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just... understand!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand what I'm saying!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.08,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kouko, just... wait a minute!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.75,0:10:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you to understand... please.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.09,0:10:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.80,0:11:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouko...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. I'm fine. Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouko...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.61,0:11:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I had too much to eat.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.74,0:11:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.95,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I swallowed it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.62,0:11:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Swallowed what?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.66,0:11:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine now, so...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouko!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did it turn out this way?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.88,0:11:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.30,0:11:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the kind of thing I'd expect from us.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what you expect of us?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.39,0:11:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I want it to be more romantic!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.15,0:11:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is how I really am.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.73,0:12:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep drawing out this side of me.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:00.24,0:12:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the one place where I can truly be myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:03.66,0:12:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I belong here more than I belong in my own room at my own house.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:10.54,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:11.71,0:12:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one I want to come home to.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.67,0:12:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've been searching for this place for a long time.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri, you've finally fallen for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have. I definitely have.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.97,0:12:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take things at our own pace.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We have plenty of time.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.81,0:12:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our second semester classes started.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.53,0:12:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was autumn.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.03,0:12:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Festival Club had begun\Npracticing for its next festival.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.45,0:12:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanagisawa Mitsuo-kun!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's apparently Banri and RoboGirl's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:57.29,golden teim,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\c&H52483E&\fnAkbar\fscx40\fscy40\b0\pos(121.41,286.485)\frz2.91}October
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:57.29,golden teim,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\c&H52483E&\fnAkbar\fscx40\fscy40\b0\frz2.91\pos(399.12,288.18)}Awa dance \Nfestival
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:57.29,golden teim,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\c&H52483E&\fnAkbar\fscx40\fscy40\b0\frz2.91\pos(121.425,523.26)}November
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:57.29,golden teim,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\c&H52483E&\fnAkbar\fscx40\fscy40\b0\frz2.91\pos(373.56,530.085)}School \Nfestival
Dialogue: 5,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Any objections or questions?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.58,0:12:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.38,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanagisawa-kun, do you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I don't.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.38,0:13:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We might finally have a chance!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.39,0:13:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll we do? What'll we do?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.76,0:13:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, I don't have a girlfriend, either. What'll you do?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.02,0:13:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not doing anything!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, looks like no one's opposed.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.48,0:13:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to work with Yanagisawa-kun, everyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.49,0:13:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot going on this fall.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.65,0:13:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,First, October.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another Awa dance festival.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,After that is the school festival in November.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.79,0:13:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be asking people from other colleges for backup there.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it everything you've got.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, start warming up!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great that you got permission, Yana-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.10,0:13:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.60,0:13:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I made Linda-senpai mad the other day.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:57.69,0:13:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouko-chan, let's warm up together.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.77,0:14:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.20,golden teim,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\c&H3F3B31&\fnAkbar\fscx80\fscy80\b0\pos(591.615,279.66)\frz4.58}October
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.20,golden teim,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\c&H3F3B31&\fnAkbar\fscx80\fscy80\b0\pos(888.045,375.06)\frz5.65}Awa dance \Nfestival
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.20,golden teim,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\c&H3F3B31&\fnAkbar\fscx80\fscy80\b0\frz2.91\pos(567.78,698.7)}November
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.20,golden teim,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\c&H3F3B31&\fnAkbar\fscx80\fscy80\b0\frz2.91\pos(840.345,855.435)\iclip(m 880.5 939 b 891 898.5 925.5 847.5 949.5 837 l 1039.5 895.5 960 1002)}School \Nfestival
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for today's practice.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.49,0:14:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dismissed.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.24,0:14:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work today!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.71,0:14:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't work.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get the chance to say a single word to her.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just getting started.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.63,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There are almost two months before the school festival.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:29.26,0:14:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've been summoned to a really secret conversation.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.47,0:14:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,About Mitsuo?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.76,0:14:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.14,0:14:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.93,0:14:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave Mitsuo to me. I'll stall him.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.56,0:14:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuo, why don't we get some tea?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? With you? Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.44,0:14:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And where are you going, Banri?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get something I forgot from campus.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feel bad making Kouko come with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you hang out with her?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.54,0:14:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us come too.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.83,0:14:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to know more about you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.00,0:15:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we want to know every last thing!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:01.75,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.84,0:15:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.46,0:15:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.80,0:15:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say anything?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.43,0:15:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What, specifically, are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't know what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.81,0:15:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Figure it out.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be unreasonable!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say that to me with that look on your face...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.86,0:15:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.90,0:15:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You kicked me!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.82,0:15:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I kicked you!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I really don't know what you meant!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so pissed about Yana-san?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's mad!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.29,0:15:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you kick my butt on the street if you weren't mad?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.29,0:15:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Those eyes! You're mad!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.38,0:15:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I'm not mad!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I s-seriously don't get it!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, you idiot?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do about this?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.40,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe how stupid you are.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, it's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.40,0:16:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm thinking from the bottom of my heart that you're a major idiot.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.16,0:16:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.99,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.87,0:16:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what campus is like after classes are over.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.71,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.38,0:16:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not mad.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just really surprised.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I got flustered.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That Yana-san came?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.27,0:16:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.56,0:16:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've told me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.69,0:16:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to avoid Yana-san so badly?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I want to avoid him.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.57,0:16:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, maybe he told you about it,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.57,0:16:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but he treated me to dinner a few times over summer break.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.82,0:16:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know about that.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:59.79,0:17:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw him a few times working at the club,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.21,0:17:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought it'd be fun to spend time with a younger guy now and then.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.13,0:17:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day, I suddenly wondered, "Why?"
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why what?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.05,0:17:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he seem so happy having dinner with me?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.14,0:17:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm being self-conscious, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.27,0:17:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck, it doesn't matter what you think of me.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:28.90,0:17:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like Yanagisawa Mitsuo saw me as something really valuable.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it was kind of scary.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.28,0:17:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.57,0:17:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A big, sweet, pedigreed dog of a guy like him?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.08,0:17:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I couldn't tell why he was interested in me.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.83,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was a fantasy, a misunderstanding, or an assumption.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.75,0:17:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way to tell.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.67,0:17:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he just likes you\N because you're attractive.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:55.13,0:17:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got a prettier face than mine,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.34,0:18:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't think I've shown him enough of my personality for him to fall in love with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.06,0:18:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't want him to think he knows me after spending so little time with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.02,0:18:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought I'd keep my distance for a while.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, today...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:14.44,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouko and I brought him to the club.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It really threw me off.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:19.78,0:18:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start by killing you.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll send Kouko after you.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was thinking during practice.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.42,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I distinctly felt that.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.67,0:18:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm just taking out my anger on you.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.05,0:18:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about kicking you in the butt earlier.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it hurt?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.05,0:18:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm totally fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm hopeless.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I always get so weird?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.73,0:18:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you're actually kind of interested in Yana-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.57,0:18:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:54.69,0:18:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really pissed at you right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you making that face?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.40,0:19:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you have a girlfriend,\N you think you can say whatever you want?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.12,0:19:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Kouko-chan seem to be getting along as well as ever.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.71,0:19:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Was she lonely while you were in Shizuoka?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.17,0:19:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she was.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.71,0:19:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.47,0:19:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.59,0:19:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom gave me her ring.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Her ring?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.97,0:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me to give it to my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.23,0:19:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to give it to her, I thought I'd wait for the right situation.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.52,0:19:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't found the right time.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the ring you were supposed to give me?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.74,0:19:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.86,0:19:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.66,0:19:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:42.45,0:19:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:48.33,0:19:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But your mom must be happy.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.42,0:19:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a girlfriend out here, and you're doing well.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.00,0:19:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I am.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.67,0:20:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you are.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some confidence in yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.05,0:20:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But I haven't been able to tell my friends yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.72,0:20:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,About my past... including you.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.98,0:20:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanagisawa Mitsuo doesn't know about us, either, does he?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.15,0:20:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to hide it.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.86,0:20:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't say anything, either.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:21.61,0:20:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want him to feel strange about you as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.12,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.41,0:20:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him everything.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.79,0:20:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:33.17,0:20:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess that's impossible.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.17,0:20:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.29,0:20:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka-chan.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing out so late?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.72,0:20:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Are you Banri's friend?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.85,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Oka Chinami.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.22,0:20:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:53.64,0:20:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head back, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka-chan, I hope we can talk sometime.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:58.36,0:20:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'd love to.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:08.20,0:21:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka-chan, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was helping some upperclassmen from the Film Club.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:13.12,0:21:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Banri, what was that about?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.87,0:21:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not right.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.34,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so close with Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.01,0:21:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same club,\N and we have a lot in common.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:26.26,0:21:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, stop.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:28.14,0:21:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the girl Yana-san likes.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.97,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not right for you to be so close to her.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:34.27,0:21:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you're acting a little weird?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.65,0:21:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for you to be so upset.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.40,0:21:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the weird one!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:39.98,0:21:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I think Kaga-san would feel bad if she saw you two just now.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.28,0:21:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel bad for Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:49.03,0:21:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the worst.
